headline: Camden Property price target raised to $130 from $128 at Piper Sandler
summary: Piper Sandler raised the firm’s price target on Camden Property (CPT) to $130 from $128 and keeps a Neutral rating on the shares. The firm sees the pre-election transaction pause giving way to a resumption of decision-making, whether leasing, capital markets, fund-raising, etc. Piper believes the direction of interest rates remains critical.
